Why's he gotta slit her throat, too?

57
00:03:31,203 --> 00:03:33,155
Um, Detective?

58
00:03:34,018 --> 00:03:35,905
When you dust the register...

59
00:03:35,905 --> 00:03:38,036
We might find your prints?

60
